<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 00:32:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡暗示哈马斯袭击与预备役军人抗议之间存在联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-suggests-link-between-hamas-attack-reservists-protest/0000018b-a133-dc0b-a1cb-e5f725340000</link><description>甘茨呼吁内塔尼亚胡撤回声明，该声明暗示在反对司法政变的抗议期间发出的拒绝预备役的呼吁可能会影响哈马斯领导人的计算</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 20:42:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-suggests-link-between-hamas-attack-reservists-protest/0000018b-a133-dc0b-a1cb-e5f725340000</guid></item><item><title>官员称以色列希望战争结束后对加沙进行安全控制</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/official-says-israel-will-want-security-control-of-gaza-after-war-ends/0000018b-a110-dc41-af9f-eb32b13b0000</link><description>政治官员计划增加进入加沙的援助，并承认限制援助是向哈马斯施压的无效方法，因为哈马斯领导层并没有被平民的苦难吓倒。一名政治官员表示，即使停火以释放人质，也只是暂时的</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 20:34:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/official-says-israel-will-want-security-control-of-gaza-after-war-ends/0000018b-a110-dc41-af9f-eb32b13b0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击一个月后，受害者家属的愤怒激起了反内塔尼亚胡的抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-05/ty-article/.highlight/a-month-into-the-war-israels-protest-movement-is-rising-again/0000018b-a07b-da24-a1cb-b77f750f0000</link><description>这一次，以色列的示威活动不是因为担心政府得逞后会发生什么，而是因为那些愿意到天涯海角寻找被绑架亲人的家庭的愤怒</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 20:23:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-05/ty-article/.highlight/a-month-into-the-war-israels-protest-movement-is-rising-again/0000018b-a07b-da24-a1cb-b77f750f0000</guid></item><item><title>对于德国犹太人来说，对加沙战争的反应带来了噩梦，以及对反犹太主义抬头的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-german-jews-reactions-to-gaza-war-bring-nightmares-fears-over-rising-antisemitism/0000018b-9fed-da24-a1cb-9fed7eb30000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日事件以来，随着反犹太主义袭击激增，德国犹太社区不得不在人身安全方面做出艰难选择，当局试图在集会自由和取缔仇恨言论之间取得平衡</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 18:57:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-german-jews-reactions-to-gaza-war-bring-nightmares-fears-over-rising-antisemitism/0000018b-9fed-da24-a1cb-9fed7eb30000</guid></item><item><title>“重要的是犹太人加入并表示巴勒斯坦人的生命与其他任何人的生命一样有价值”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-important-that-jews-say-that-a-palestinian-life-is-worth-the-same-as-any-other-life/0000018b-a039-dc0b-a1cb-e5ff92280000</link><description>周六，数千名抗议者在法国首都游行，呼吁加沙立即停火。虽然大多数抗议者来自亲巴勒斯坦团体和左派，但也有少数犹太人在那里“抗议和平”</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 18:11:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-important-that-jews-say-that-a-palestinian-life-is-worth-the-same-as-any-other-life/0000018b-a039-dc0b-a1cb-e5ff92280000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军事训练基地的拉比称“整个国家”都是“我们的”，包括加沙和黎巴嫩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/rabbi-at-israeli-military-base-says-whole-country-is-ours-including-gaza-and-lebanon/0000018b-a031-d42c-a9ef-ad772cdc0000</link><description>陆军表示，阿米查·弗里德曼的言论与其价值观不符，此前他告诉士兵，以色列将使其在加沙的前定居点看起来“很小”</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 17:06:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/rabbi-at-israeli-military-base-says-whole-country-is-ours-including-gaza-and-lebanon/0000018b-a031-d42c-a9ef-ad772cdc0000</guid></item><item><title>Amalia Dayan 在纽约从未遇到过反犹太主义 然后到了 10 月 7 日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/amalia-dayan-defends-israel-from-n-y-c-israel-has-terrible-public-relations/0000018b-909c-db7e-af9b-fbdf30b80000</link><description>以色列达扬王朝的艺术品经销商阿玛莉亚·达扬 (Amalia Dayan) 24 岁时移居纽约，并成功开设了一家画廊。艺术界的公开信谴责以色列，却忽略了 10 月 7 日的大屠杀，这让她为自己人民的叙述而奋斗：“以色列的公共关系很糟糕，”她告诉《国土报》</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 15:05:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/amalia-dayan-defends-israel-from-n-y-c-israel-has-terrible-public-relations/0000018b-909c-db7e-af9b-fbdf30b80000</guid></item><item><title>Twitter 的社区注释如何加速否认哈马斯针对以色列人的暴行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/twitters-community-notes-accelerates-denialism-about-hamas-atrocities-against-israelis/0000018b-9f5b-dbad-abfb-dfdf31200000</link><description>社区笔记功能原本是为了消除 X（以前的 Twitter）上的阴谋论。相反，埃隆·马斯克对众包审核的偏爱是允许恶意用户将有关 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击的仇恨、谎言和虚假信息武器化</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 14:36:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/twitters-community-notes-accelerates-denialism-about-hamas-atrocities-against-israelis/0000018b-9f5b-dbad-abfb-dfdf31200000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争引发的美国校园反犹太主义给即将上大学的犹太孩子带来了困境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-campus-antisemitism-over-gaza-war-creates-dilemma-for-college-bound-jewish-kids/0000018b-9fa8-dbad-abfb-dffce13d0000</link><description>犹太高中生和他们的父母正面临着前所未有的困境：要么安于一所不太知名的大学，在那里他们会觉得作为犹太人更安全，要么瞄准最好的学校，因为他们知道等待他们的可能是充满敌意的校园经历</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 14:34:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-campus-antisemitism-over-gaza-war-creates-dilemma-for-college-bound-jewish-kids/0000018b-9fa8-dbad-abfb-dffce13d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-哈马斯战争近距离：与以色列国防军一起进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-is-what-war-looks-and-sounds-like-a-journey-into-gaza-with-the-idf/0000018b-9f5f-db51-a99b-9fdf49090000</link><description>四周无休无止的破坏，空袭和坦克炮弹的配乐：《国土报》加入加沙地带北部第 36 师的士兵队伍</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 14:28:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-is-what-war-looks-and-sounds-like-a-journey-into-gaza-with-the-idf/0000018b-9f5f-db51-a99b-9fdf49090000</guid></item><item><title>他用迷人的照片记录了他的军队服役经历。上周他在加沙去世</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-documented-his-army-service-in-captivating-photos-last-week-his-died-in-gaza/0000018b-9f43-dbad-abfb-dfdfae330000</link><description>以色列参谋军士。 20 岁的拉维·利普希茨 (Lavi Lipshitz) 于上周二在加沙的行动中身亡。这位才华横溢的摄影爱好者在去世前创建了一个 Instagram 页面，展示了用他的富士相机捕捉他服兵役的精彩照片</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 13:30:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-documented-his-army-service-in-captivating-photos-last-week-his-died-in-gaza/0000018b-9f43-dbad-abfb-dfdfae330000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼议员呼吁停止西岸橄榄收获</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-far-right-lawmaker-calls-to-halt-west-bank-olive-harvest/0000018b-9f44-d27d-a9fb-dfed5d640002</link><description>最近被任命为以色列议会约旦河西岸问题小组委员会主席的兹维·苏科特 (Zvi Sukkot) 援引巴勒斯坦工人的话说，他们曾协助哈马斯袭击</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 12:02:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-far-right-lawmaker-calls-to-halt-west-bank-olive-harvest/0000018b-9f44-d27d-a9fb-dfed5d640002</guid></item><item><title>以色列著名电影制片人阿里·福尔曼抨击西方对哈马斯暴行“无知”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/renowned-israeli-filmmaker-ari-folman-slams-wests-hypocrisy-and-unawareness-about-hamas/0000018b-9f14-d510-a1af-ff5cba940000</link><description>屡获殊荣的《与巴希尔跳华尔兹》导演开始拍摄哈马斯人质家人的证词，批评以色列政府在战争第一周的忽视：“没有人与他们交谈”</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 11:29:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/renowned-israeli-filmmaker-ari-folman-slams-wests-hypocrisy-and-unawareness-about-hamas/0000018b-9f14-d510-a1af-ff5cba940000</guid></item><item><title>“我们几乎看不到恐怖分子。他们在地下”：与以色列士兵在加沙地面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-barely-see-terrorists-theyre-underground-in-gaza-with-israeli-soldiers/0000018b-9ecf-d8a6-a38b-dedf23810000</link><description>以色列对加沙地带发动地面进攻八天后，以色列国防军作战士兵知道最艰难的战斗即将到来</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 11:10:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-barely-see-terrorists-theyre-underground-in-gaza-with-israeli-soldiers/0000018b-9ecf-d8a6-a38b-dedf23810000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长召开重要司法任命委员会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-to-convene-key-judicial-appointments-committee/0000018b-9f0a-dbad-abfb-dfde5e990000</link><description>自 2022 年晚些时候重新掌权以来，司法部长亚里夫·莱文 (Yariv Levin) 一直拒绝这样做，但他宣布将在 15 天内召开关键委员会会议</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 10:50:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-to-convene-key-judicial-appointments-committee/0000018b-9f0a-dbad-abfb-dfde5e990000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡批评部长建议“选择”向加沙投掷核弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/netanyahu-criticizes-minister-who-suggested-option-of-dropping-nuclear-bomb-on-gaza/0000018b-9e7b-db71-a7df-ffffe4510000</link><description>极右翼部长阿米柴·埃利亚胡声称加沙地带没有非战斗人员，后来说他的言论是“比喻性的”，但内塔尼亚胡总理禁止他参加政府会议</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 08:02:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/netanyahu-criticizes-minister-who-suggested-option-of-dropping-nuclear-bomb-on-gaza/0000018b-9e7b-db71-a7df-ffffe4510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队准备进入加沙城，特拉维夫遭到猛烈炮击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-live/u-s-efforts-for-a-ceasefire-increase-as-israeli-forces-make-their-way-deeper-into-gaza/0000018b-9d1a-d27d-a9fb-dfbbfcc60000</link><description>以色列军队称，有 29 名士兵和军官在持续的地面攻势中丧生 ■ 布林肯在拉马拉会见阿巴斯，此前他表示，美国和阿拉伯国家同意哈马斯控制的加沙现状不能继续下去 ■ 黎巴嫩发射的导弹击中以色列北部，造成一人受伤 ■ 哈马斯：超过 60 人人质因以色列对加沙的空袭而失踪 ■ 加沙有 242 名人质被扣押，40 人仍然失踪 ■ 至少 1,300 名平民和士兵在哈马斯大屠杀中丧生 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙有 9,000 多人丧生</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 04:39:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article-live/u-s-efforts-for-a-ceasefire-increase-as-israeli-forces-make-their-way-deeper-into-gaza/0000018b-9d1a-d27d-a9fb-dfbbfcc60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列新的政治秩序将从 10 月 7 日崩溃的深渊中崛起</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/from-the-abyss-of-the-october-7-debacle-a-new-israeli-political-order-will-rise/0000018b-9b89-dbad-abfb-dbdd02fd0000</link><description>与赎罪日战争引发的政治转变类似，10 月 7 日将宣告利库德集团长期统治的结束。以色列新政府中不会有极端分子的地位</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 03:57:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/from-the-abyss-of-the-october-7-debacle-a-new-israeli-political-order-will-rise/0000018b-9b89-dbad-abfb-dbdd02fd0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管以色列猛烈袭击，哈马斯领导层仍保持对加沙的控制</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/despite-israels-fierce-attacks-hamas-leadership-maintains-control-on-gaza/0000018b-9c11-d27d-a9fb-deb916c20000</link><description>随着加沙战事愈演愈烈，以色列国防军的重点必须是拆除哈马斯地道。 ■ 人们可以感觉到美国对以色列的耐心正在减弱，因为国务卿布林肯呼吁允许增加对加沙的援助，并指出暂停战斗将导致美国对以色列的耐心逐渐减弱。帮助释放人质</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 03:56:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-05/ty-article/.premium/despite-israels-fierce-attacks-hamas-leadership-maintains-control-on-gaza/0000018b-9c11-d27d-a9fb-deb916c20000</guid></item><item><title>从也门向以色列发射导弹：史无前例的发射、史无前例的拦截</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-05/ty-article/missile-from-yemen-to-israel-unprecedented-launch-unprecedented-interception/0000018b-8f88-d7a8-afcf-afab9c5e0000</link><description>伊朗本周从也门发射到埃拉特的导弹——距离至少 1,600 公里——打破了两项记录：从地面炮台发射弹道导弹的最远射程，以及以色列“箭”导弹防御系统首次对弹道导弹进行实战拦截系统</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 03:16:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-05/ty-article/missile-from-yemen-to-israel-unprecedented-launch-unprecedented-interception/0000018b-8f88-d7a8-afcf-afab9c5e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>